# Summary
This documentation explains how to implement Amplitude Session Replay using Google Tag Manager (GTM), which requires a different procedure than the standard Browser SDK Plugin, including enabling the Session Replay toggle in the Amplitude Analytics Browser SDK template and configuring settings in Amplitude's organization settings.

